<p><span class="headers">May 18, 2002 - </span>
<p>
Just a quick note to let folks know that I've changed links around since the last front page update. The main May 8, 2002 recipes page can still be found in the same spot, but ALL cultural recipes have been moved to their <a href="http://eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g67&menustr=080040000000">permanent links off the cultural recipes page</a>. In another week or so, I hope to split out the May 8, 2002 recipes onto thier permanent recipes pages. I'll also be redoing FAQs and trade supplies listings as time permits.</p>
